SqlText: select [OBBQ].[OnHandQty] as [Quantity],[OBTN].[ExpDate] as [Bbd],[OBTN].[DistNumber] as [Batch],[OBIN].[AbsEntry] as [BinAbsEntry],[OBIN].[BarCode] as [BinBarCode],[OBIN].[BinCode] as [BinCode] from [OBBQ],[OBTN],[OBIN] where [OBBQ].[SnBMDAbs] = [OBTN].[AbsEntry] and [OBBQ].[BinAbs] = [OBIN].[AbsEntry] and [OBBQ].[ItemCode] = :itemCode and [OBBQ].[BinAbs] = :binAbsEntry and [OBBQ].[OnHandQty] > 0 order by [OBTN].[DistNumber]
